# OS / editor noise (recursive — `.DS_Store` is macOS, drops itself
# in every directory the user opens in Finder)
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
.vscode/

# build outputs (workspace and per-package)
target/
*/target/

# Per-run fixtures the mdbook preprocessor materialises into a book's
# tree at build time. The inner test-book under mdbook-rustviz/ is
# the canonical worked example; its src/examples and book/ outputs
# are regenerated on every `mdbook build` so we don't track them.
mdbook-rustviz/test-book/src/examples
mdbook-rustviz/test-book/book

# Frontend build artifacts (produced by setup.sh / npm run build)
playground/frontend/dist/
playground/frontend/node_modules/
playground/frontend/*.tsbuildinfo
